title: Young Guns, Trading Teddy Bridgewater, and an MVP Injury | GM Street (Ep. 283)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier link up to discuss the injury Nick Foles sustained in New England (02:00), the Jets' QB situation (12:00), Pittsburgh's messy loss to the Packers (22:45), and young quarterbacks around the league (31:45).
